{"tid":2257842,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"630人睇協恩網上入學講座","createTime":"2020-10-25T14:06:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-25T14:06:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"38b4bab221dcf8924f7d5d5cc11e2b4d41e97ab7","tid":2257842,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T14:06:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201025/R4CIJZBJQJFXHD2XDU32HH35C4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201025%2FR4CIJZBJQJFXHD2XDU32HH35C4%2F&d=FHegwWfkEdb3mv0CWz72PYL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=c09146ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201025%2FR4CIJZBJQJFXHD2XDU32HH35C4%2F&h=eb49cc42\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201025/R4CIJZBJQJFXHD2XDU32HH35C4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n630人睇協恩網上入學講座<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/wKQ2lrJfH0djTMzozrRebI9wKOk=/720x461/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CDOCHZGULZCY3BUNOEK5NA3N5M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FwKQ2lrJfH0djTMzozrRebI9wKOk%3D%2F720x461%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCDOCHZGULZCY3BUNOEK5NA3N5M.jpg&h=59f943e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁少儀<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】現正值直資中學招生高峯期，受疫情影響，普遍學校採用網上形式進行講座。傳統直資名女校協恩中學昨舉行網上中一入學簡介會，高峯期收看人數約630人。校長梁少儀強調，協恩重視知識傳授與學術成果，寄語家長，縱然期望女兒能學有所成，學校對「成功」的看法是「學生須找到學習、工作、生命的意義，懂得知道自己在『家、國、社會』的重要性。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n校長盼學生覓生命意義<br />\n<br />\n協恩提供180個中一學額，應試學生須參與筆試，首輪面試11月28日舉行，悉數面見所有申請人，疫潮下可能改用網上形式進行。個人面見環節，老師將透過不同問題了解學生表達、理解、解難、運算、創意等能力。協恩的音樂、體藝比賽表現一直稱霸學界，簡介會透露，學生若想表現運動能力，可揀選最「拿手」的兩項技能測試。音樂方面，面試會要求學生演繹一首樂章及設視奏部份，最重要看學生對音樂的個人看法。<br />\n<br />\n助理校長周希怡預計次輪。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n取錄結果明年3月下旬公佈，候補生名單會於5月1日或以前寄出。梁少儀強調，協。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n該校自2012年轉為直資，增加資源以聘用更多教師推行小組教學，以及六年師友計劃等。現時初中學費為35,955元。梁說，為傳承學校創校以來照顧各階層女生的傳統，特別將學費收入三成撥作獎助學金。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jggAuydmYG2eewuq3GCiyFwqIKU=/1228x948/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KJIPA4MG75H6ZNEOYZKDDWAO7I.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FjggAuydmYG2eewuq3GCiyFwqIKU%3D%2F1228x948%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKJIPA4MG75H6ZNEOYZKDDWAO7I.gif&h=3311641a&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}